templates.  The policies and templates can be found at:

  http://sourceforge.net/projects/pods

====

Name:         visualization
Maintainers:  Hordur Johannsson <hordurj@csail.mit.edu>
Summary:      Tools for visualization of SLAM algorithms.
Description:
  This pod contains tools for visualization of SLAM algorithms. This
  includes rendering posegraphs and sensor data like point clouds.

Requirements: 
  LCM (http://lcm.googlecode.com)
  libbot2 (svn checkout https://svn.csail.mit.edu/libbot2)

License:      No license available

